#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""Thin entry point that delegates to ``cmuts.visualize.plotting:main``.

Renders all standard figures (profiles, heatmap, coverage, termination, mutual
information, SNR-vs-depth, ...) from a reactivity HDF5 file written by
